description: Just before the Great Darkness men constructed time capsules to preserve of knowledge. To open these crypts of knowledge a key is needed, the pursuit of which, by the cult of the Black Moon, crosses several times the life of Brendon.
name: La Luna Nera
Cip & Ciop e la magia di una giornata di pioggia

description: Hired by the young Tessa Stevenson to discover who or what killed her father, Brendon is in Arkhem. Recently, in town of the Dorset region strange facts happen: people burnt alive by a dragon and other mysteriously disappeared. In the city lives an alchemist, Trevanian, who has found a way to take advantage of the hot vapors of the underground that would bring warmth throughout the city, using the old sewer system.
name: Le ali della notte
Cip & Ciop e la festa di primavera
Cip & Ciop e la mongolfiera sospetta
I Gialli di Cip & Ciop - Le noci rubate

volume.name: Les classiques du dessin animé en bande dessinée
Les classiques du dessin animé en bande dessinée

description: The long-simmering rivalry between Zatanna and The Spectre ignites in this issue! In an infernal courtroom beneath Alcatraz Prison, the Maid of Magic is on trial for her life, with the vengeful Spectre determined to find her just as guilty as the mystic criminals she fights. Will even Zatanna's powers be enough to save her from God's wrath?
name: Witch Hunt

description: Deep below one of the most prestigious universities in the DCU lie some deadly secrets that Supergirl is determined to expose! But if she uses her powers, she'll blow her cover, thus ruining any chance she and Lois Lane have of catching the madman responsible for it all!
name: This is Not My Life, Part 2 of 3

description: Moon is the thirteenth zodiac sign that humanity has for too long forgotten. While he was investigating this thirteenth sign, Sergej Orloff mysteriously disappeared. His girlfriend, Monique, is unaware of Sergei’s many criminal activities, and thinks that he and Martin Mystere are still good friend. So Monique addresses the Detective of the Impossible to find her missing companion.
name: Il tredicesimo segno

description: Saturn Queen triumphant? With the Legion on the ropes, it sure looks that way. Plus: if you thought issue #11's Timber Wolf/Sun Emperor fight burned your fingertips, you ain't seen nuthin' til you've seen Sun Boy versus Sun Killer!
name: False Victory

description: Naples, Italy: the evil Sergej Orloff has managed to get hold of an old parchment found in the excavations of Pompeii. Martin Mystere, also in Naples to follow this story, clashes with some gangsters who do not want an investigation into the origin of the mysterious document. Martin and Java, not at all intimidated, continue their research until they find, in the ruins of Pompeii, a secret passage.
name: Il segreto di Pulcinella

description: The Detective of the Impossible clashes with a clan of gangsters who want to hide the presence of an ancient Atlantean base located at Lake Averno . The criminals , who have been aware of it for some time and who exploit it for their own sinister purposes , are also willing to kill in order to keep the secret , and to Martin and Java there seems no escape. But an unexpected help can still come from their enemy Sergej Orloff .
name: La smorfia napoletana

description: Martin accepts a new job and moves to Florence, in Italy, with Java. Meanwhile, the discovery of the tomb of the Egyptian architect Imhotep sets off the search of an unidentified town named Rym Thwt , guarded by the incredible powers of a magical object : the Tear of Thoth .
name: Nea Heliopolis

description: Martin Mystere is in Italy to record a series of television programs devoted to " Italian Mysteries " and , for some time , he will live in Florence , in Via dell'Anguillara . Upon arriving , the Detective of the Impossible is just struggling with a mystery tied to ancient Egypt , but , just in his new country , he will find its solution: the discovery of the location of Nea Heliapolis , also known as the secret city of Thwt Rym .
name: Welcome to Italy

description: The American writer William Burroughs comes in possession of an unpublished manuscript by Giordano Bruno, about the existence of an old "machine", able to control the human mind, which would be in Rome. Burroughs asks Martin to find and destroy it before it falls into the wrong hands. In fact, Sergei Orloff and the Men in Black are both interested in the discovery of this object.
name: Catacombe!

description: In Piazza Vittorio, in Rome , from 1660 there is an " alchemical door " that leads to nowhere and is covered with inscriptions never deciphered . This monument is one of the clues that bring Martin and Orloff in the place where the Wonderful Machine , a special device named by Giordano Bruno in his unpublished writings , is hidden. To retrieve it , the Men in Black do not hesitate to blackmail both the detective and his archenemy.
name: Il teatro della memoria
The Case of the Murdering Tiger
Five Passengers In Search of an Author
Terrible Terry Gill aka Wanted, One Child
The Crown of the Mayas; The Invisible Intruder

volume.name: Walt Disney's Uncle Scrooge Adventures In Color

description: X-Factor headquarters is under siege! As the birth of Wolfsbane’s baby draws near, demonic forces pound at their door, desperate to steal the child away. How will X-Factor battle the supernatural? Salvation may just arrive in a very familiar form…
